'cause...
things are getting serious.

39:08.563 --> 39:10.565
<i>Well, I'm happy for you.</i>

39:10.609 --> 39:12.567
<i>And when you decide to ask,</i>

39:12.611 --> 39:15.831
<i>there are some really beautiful
venues out here in Japan.</i>

39:15.875 --> 39:18.225
<i>Destination weddings
are all the rage right now.</i>

39:18.268 --> 39:19.008
♪ High, low

39:19.052 --> 39:20.140
Thank you, buddy.

39:20.183 --> 39:21.489
<i>Arigato.</i>

39:21.533 --> 39:23.970
♪ High, low

39:24.013 --> 39:26.146
I had no idea
you would stoop this low.

39:26.189 --> 39:27.408
Okay, hold on, hold on.

39:27.452 --> 39:29.976
I-I tried to have
a conversation with you,

39:30.019 --> 39:31.586
but you left me
no choice.

39:31.630 --> 39:33.806
I did what I thought
was best for Lila.

39:33.849 --> 39:35.373
Congratulations.

39:35.416 --> 39:37.592
Penelope and I broke up
and Lila is devastated.

39:37.636 --> 39:39.986
You broke up?
That's not what I was --

39:40.029 --> 39:41.988
Oh, please.

39:42.031 --> 39:43.555
It's exactly
what you wanted.

39:43.598 --> 39:46.862
The move is off.
You won.

39:46.906 --> 39:49.343
Okay, look, I'm sorry,
but I did what I had to do

39:49.387 --> 39:50.997
to stay in
my daughter's life.

39:51.040 --> 39:53.260
You were doing the same thing,
digging into my past.

39:53.303 --> 39:55.567
Because your past has actually
harmed our daughter.

39:55.610 --> 39:57.569
Penelope's had nothing to do
with anything.

39:57.612 --> 39:58.744
Then why'd you break up
with her?

39:58.787 --> 40:01.181
Because she didn't tell me.

40:01.224 --> 40:04.750
And I can't be with
another woman who lies to me.

40:06.273 --> 40:07.970
I guess there's no telling
when we'll be rid of

40:08.014 --> 40:09.145
the alarm system.

40:09.189 --> 40:10.669
No, but if Abril
wants me dead,

40:10.712 --> 40:12.497
I doubt that thing's
gonna stop her.

40:12.540 --> 40:14.673
She killed eight armed men
by herself.

40:19.199 --> 40:20.113
Hello?

40:20.156 --> 40:21.767
<i>Buenos días.</i>

40:24.030 --> 40:25.771
Abril, where are you?

40:25.814 --> 40:27.381
I just crossed the border.

40:27.425 --> 40:29.383
In 20 minutes,
I'll be on a plane back home.

40:29.427 --> 40:31.167
How's the baby?

40:31.211 --> 40:32.647
None of your business.

40:32.691 --> 40:34.997
What? You don't think
I would hurt him? Or you?

40:35.041 --> 40:36.825
I spent my day wading through
dead bodies.

40:36.869 --> 40:38.697
There's nothing
I'd put past you.

40:38.740 --> 40:40.438
Oh, no, that was just business,
you know?

40:40.481 --> 40:42.048
Unlike La Fiera,

40:42.091 --> 40:46.618
<i>I kill only when it's
strategically advantageous.</i>

40:46.661 --> 40:48.968
But killing a police detective
and her family --

40:49.011 --> 40:52.537
No, that is bad business,
and it will stay that way,

40:52.580 --> 40:54.669
<i>unless you come after me
in Guatemala.</i>

40:54.713 --> 40:56.758
I'm good here. <i>
Bueno.</i>

40:56.802 --> 40:59.152
Then this is goodbye.

41:04.113 --> 41:06.638
So, do you see
anything you like?

41:06.681 --> 41:08.640
Um, everything.

41:08.683 --> 41:10.511
I'm warning you right now,
I will be photographing

41:10.555 --> 41:12.731
all of our food.
Go for it.

41:15.037 --> 41:18.127
So...

41:18.171 --> 41:20.869
I've been thinking a lot
about us lately.

41:22.131 --> 41:23.785
Me too.

41:23.829 --> 41:26.571
- You're a pretty decent roommate.
- Thanks.

41:26.614 --> 41:29.835
And you are
a super good kisser.

41:29.878 --> 41:32.751
And the fact
of the matter is,

41:32.794 --> 41:34.709
I'm in love with you.

41:36.276 --> 41:37.538
Thank God.

41:37.582 --> 41:40.062
'Cause I'm in love
with you, too.

41:46.025 --> 41:47.679
Bailey.

41:47.722 --> 41:48.854
Jason.

41:48.897 --> 41:50.856
I --

41:50.899 --> 41:52.292
When did they
let you out?

41:52.335 --> 41:55.164
Uh, last week.

41:55.208 --> 41:56.557
Uh, who are you?

41:56.601 --> 41:57.645
I'm John Nolan,
her boyfriend.

41:57.689 --> 41:59.081
And you are?

41:59.125 --> 42:01.257
Uh, her husband.
